                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                    <div class="courses-item d-flex flex-column bg-white overflow-hidden h-100">
                        <div class="text-center p-4 pt-0">
                            <div class="d-inline-block bg-primary text-white fs-5 py-1 px-4 mb-4"></div>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Annonce</h5>
                            <p>Ayez l'occasion de poster vos annonces en fonction de vos voitures.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="position-relative mt-auto">
                            <img class="img-fluid" src={{"assets/img/annonce.jpg"}} alt="">
                            <div class="courses-overlay">
                                <a class="btn btn-outline-primary border-2" href={{ path('annonce')}}>Voir plus</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
